{"route":{"route":"/posts/854ed6ec/","outputPath":"posts/854ed6ec/index.html","kind":"post","title":"c语言数组输出的另一种方法","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"854ed6ec"}},"description":"今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:一个有趣的C语言程序 int x[5],x实际上保存的是这个数组首元素的地址也就是&x[0]. a[x]的等效写法是\\ (a+&x).因为上面说了x实际上是x[0]. 所以可以进一步写成\\ (a+&x[0]),又因为a=1所以可以替换成\\ (&x[0]+1),也就是x[1]. 所以就是x","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/c语言数组输出的另一种方法.md","route":"/posts/854ed6ec/","abbrlink":"854ed6ec","title":"c语言数组输出的另一种方法","date":"2017-12-10 10:39:54","updated":"2017-12-10 10:39:54","tags":["C"],"categories":["Program"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:<a href=\"http://blog.accut.cn/archives/173\">一个有趣的C语言程序</a></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-c\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">#include</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> &#x3C;stdio.h></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> </span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">int</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">()</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">{</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    int</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> a </span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 1</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    int</span><span style=\"color:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70\"> x</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">[</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">5</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">]</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">{</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">1</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">2</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">3</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">4</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">5</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">};</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">    printf</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">(</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">%d</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70\">a</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">[x]);</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    return</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">output:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 2</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>int x[5],x实际上保存的是这个数组首元素的地址也就是&amp;x[0].<br>\na[x]的等效写法是*(a+&amp;x).因为上面说了x实际上是x[0].<br>\n所以可以进一步写成*(a+&amp;x[0]),又因为a=1所以可以替换成*(&amp;x[0]+1),也就是x[1].<br>\n所以就是x[1]对应的值：2</p>\n<p>由此我又想到了二位数组</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-c\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">#include</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> &#x3C;stdio.h></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> </span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">int</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">()</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">{</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    int</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> a </span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 1</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    int</span><span style=\"color:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70\"> x</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">[</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">2</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">][</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">2</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">]</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">{{</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">1</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">2</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">},{</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">3</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">4</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">}};</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">    printf</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">(</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">%d</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70\">a</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">[</span><span style=\"color:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70\">a</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">[x]]);</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    return</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">output:</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 4</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>感觉好神奇,而且在之前不知道在哪看到__c语言的数组其实就是指针的合集__,而且最近要用链表,更觉得链表和数组差不多.</p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"854ed6ec","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}